data.description: Here's your chance to own a lovely two story home in the Haight Village Historic District! This unique beauty offers 1692 sq. ft. of charming living space on two levels with a full basement, deck and welcoming porch! Huge windows offer lots of natural light on the main level where you find a living room, dining room, parlor, half bath, bonus room & kitchen. The upper level has a huge primary bedroom with walk-in closet and access to an upper porch, plus two other bedrooms and a full bath. An enclosed porch leads to the side deck and fenced backyard. The adjoining fenced lot with a playhouse goes with the house. Some tlc needed. Bring your decorating ideas! New furnace & AC 2023. Sold "As Is"
